<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Job Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>New Job Notification</h2>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>A new job has been added:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Title:</strong> {{ job.getTitle() }}</li>
        <li><strong>Description:</strong> {{ job.getDescription() }}</li>
        <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> {{ job.getDeadline()|date('Y-m-d') }}</li>
        <li><strong>Type:</strong> {{ job.getType() }}</li>
        <li><strong>Salary:</strong> {{ job.getSalary() }}</li>
        <!-- You can include more details as needed -->
    </ul>

    <p>Thank you for using our platform.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Your Platform Team</p>
</body>
</html>
